STARability exists to transform the lives of individuals with disabilities through social, vocational, and educational connections to the community, while strengthening awareness and respect for individual abilities. 

Ways in which the organization makes a difference in participants lives include the Trailblazer Academy — a pioneering outreach program which offers community-based skill development experiences for young adults, whether they are on a path to life enrichment or have vocational aspirations. 

The nonprofit organization also holds classes and workshops, has a yearly fundraising gala and features retail outlets, The STAR Store and STAR Studio.

📢 Attention, please! 📢 Join me in making a difference for our community…

I would like to share something that is close to my heart . I have become deeply involved with Project Outreach of Naples(501c3) that was founded in 2009 by Angela Meister and Julie Thomas.
They have partnered with churches and local nonprofits to feed, clothe, repair, heal, and provide resources to those that are in need the most.
Their passionate group of volunteers, inspired by the teachings of Jesus, work tirelessly to bring unity and change in our community in which I have seen firsthand. After volunteering and getting involved directly with Angela & Julie I knew I wanted to do a lot more to help this organization. 
 
 🌟🌟🌟🌟🌟🌟🌟🌟🌟🌟🌟🌟🌟🌟🌟

Last year I was fortunate to host our first Winter Wonderland Gala , with my cohosts, Erica Current and Christine Marie, where we raised over $75.000.🙏
Since then, I have become a board member with Project Outreach  and have gotten even more involved !

The ultimate vision is to build a Dream Center that will have Affordable Housing for service people (nurses, teachers, EMT’s, police officers, veterans, etc.), a community center, an education building, a clinic, a church, and a veteran’s place.
We can’t wait to show the plans at the Gala ✨ . 
 

Our ELEVATE GALA this year will be on :

Friday December 8th  at 6 pm 

📍Jet 1 | 101 aviation dr. 

It will be a night filled with purpose, passion & fun. 

If you’re interested in attending, impacting by sponsoring the event, or just spreading the word, your consideration would mean the world to me 🙏.

Thank you, everyone, for your tremendous efforts in making our community better. Together, we’re creating a real difference!🌟🤗🙌

Please click on the link below for more information: https://www.projectoutreachnaples.com/naples-winter-gala-2023.html
